保安部門在2010年4月開始準備峰會期間的保安工作。峰會保安將由{{link-en|多倫多警察部|Toronto Police Service}}、[[安大略省警察局|安大略省省警]]（OPP）以及[[加拿大皇家騎警|加拿大皇家騎警]]（RCMP）負責，而{{link-en|皮爾區警察部|Peel Regional Police}}將於坐落[[密西沙加|密西沙加]]市的[[多倫多皮爾遜國際機場|多倫多皮爾遜國際機場]]協助各國政要抵境和離境時的保安工作。該四個保安部門並組成一個{{link-en|綜合保安部隊|Integrated Security Unit}}；類似安排亦曾應用於[[溫哥華|溫哥華]][[2010年冬季奧運會|2010年冬季奧運會]]。國内其他警察部門亦有提供警力，包括{{link-en|約克區警察部|York Regional Police}}、{{link-en|荷頓區警察部|Halton Regional Police}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/2010/06/22/peter-kuitenbrouwer-downtown-doesnt-feel-like-home-during-g20/|title=Peter Kuitenbrouwer: Downtown doesn’t feel like home during G20|3=|accessdate=2010-06-28|archive-date=2012-07-03|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120703180037/http://news.nationalpost.com/2010/06/22/peter-kuitenbrouwer-downtown-doesnt-feel-like-home-during-g20/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、{{link-en|巴里警察部|Barrie Police Service}}、{{link-en|滑鐵盧區警察部|Waterloo Regional Police}}、{{link-en|尼亞加拉區警察部|Niagara Regional Police}}、{{link-en|咸美頓警察部|Hamilton Police Service}}、{{link-en|卡加利警察部|Calgary Police Service}}<ref>{{cite web |author=Calgary Herald June 14, 2010 |url=http://www.calgaryherald.com/news/Calgary+police+head+Toronto+massive+security+effort/3150428/story.html |title=Calgary police head to Toronto for massive G20 security effort |publisher=Calgaryherald.com |date=2010-06-14 |accessdate=2010-06-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100617181350/http://www.calgaryherald.com/news/Calgary+police+head+Toronto+massive+security+effort/3150428/story.html |archivedate=2010-06-17 }}</ref>、以及{{link-en|滿地可警察部|Service de police de la Ville de Montréal}}。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.insidetoronto.com/news/article/839309--protesters-gather-at-allan-gardens-to-oppose-g20-summit |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-03-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120229170723/http://www.insidetoronto.com/news/article/839309--protesters-gather-at-allan-gardens-to-oppose-g20-summit |archivedate=2012-02-29 }}</ref>

據《[[環球郵報|環球郵報]]》報道，峰會期間將有約一萬名軍裝警員、一千名護衛員和數支加拿大軍部部隊維持治安。<ref name="mondaq1">{{cite web |url=http://www.mondaq.com/canada/article.asp?articleid=99928 |title=Canada, Labour and Employment, Toronto G8 and G20 Summits â€“ Employer Planning Issues - Bennett Jones LLP - 06/05/2010, Health & Safety |publisher=Mondaq.com |date=2010-05-06 |accessdate=2010-05-20 |archive-date=2010-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100529210007/http://www.mondaq.com/canada/article.asp?articleid=99928 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[北美空防司令部|北美空防司令部]]於2010年5月6日至7日在[[大多倫多地區|大多倫多地區]]上空進行演習<ref>{{cite web |author=Canada |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/g8-g20/blog-local-view/its-a-bird-its-a-plane-its-a-terrifying-display-of-military-might/article1558886/ |title=It's a bird, it's a plane, it's a terrifying display of military might |publisher=The Globe and Mail |date=2010-05-06 |accessdate=2010-05-20 |archive-date=2010-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100511031943/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/g8-g20/blog-local-view/its-a-bird-its-a-plane-its-a-terrifying-display-of-military-might/article1558886/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而峰會期間多倫多上空亦將設有飛行管制。亨茨維爾G-8峰會和多倫多G-20峰會的保安費用於5月尾時估計合共達9億3000萬[[加元|加元]]，由加拿大聯邦政府承擔。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://toronto.ctv.ca/servlet/an/local/CTVNews/20100528/g8-g20-costs-page-100528/20100528/?hub=TorontoNewHome|title=Security chief defends cost of G8-G20|3=|accessdate=2010-06-04|archive-date=2010-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100530062200/http://toronto.ctv.ca/servlet/an/local/CTVNews/20100528/g8-g20-costs-page-100528/20100528/?hub=TorontoNewHome|dead-url=no}}</ref>

{{link-en|大多市會議中心|Metro Toronto Convention Centre}}一帶限制車輛和行人出入，管制區北界為{{link-en|國王街|King Street}}、南界為{{link-en|湖濱大道|Lake Shore Boulevard}}、東界為[[央街|央街]]、西界為[[士巴丹拿道|士巴丹拿道]]和藍鳥路。<ref name="mondaq1"/>會議中心本身則會被圍欄包圍，市民和示威者不得進出。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://thestar.blogs.com/g20/2010/05/details-of-g20-red-zone-announced.html |title=Details of G20 fence announced |publisher=TheStar.com |date=2010-05-28 |accessdate=2010-05-28 |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930160649/https://thestar.blogs.com/g20/2010/05/details-of-g20-red-zone-announced.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>多倫多警察部並於區内設置77部[[閉路電視|閉路電視]]鏡頭，峰會過去將被拆除。位於{{link-en|東方大道|Eastern Avenue (Toronto)}}的一間電影片場將於峰會期間用作扣留被捕人士之用。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://toronto.ctv.ca/servlet/an/local/CTVNews/20100511/G20-Protest-100511/20100511/?hub=TorontoNewHome |title=CTV Toronto - Protesters prepare for G20 demonstrations - CTV News |publisher=Toronto.ctv.ca |date= |accessdate=2010-05-20 |archive-date=2012-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310050941/http://toronto.ctv.ca/servlet/an/local/CTVNews/20100511/G20-Protest-100511/20100511/?hub=TorontoNewHome |dead-url=no }}</ref>多倫多警察部曾一度打算將{{link-en|聖三一貝活公園|Trinity Bellwoods Park}}定作示威區，但在居民強烈反對之下將示威區調往{{link-en|女王公園 (多倫多)|Queen's Park (Toronto)|女王公園}}北邊。位於[[加拿大博覽會|加拿大博覽會]]會場的Direct Energy Centre將被用作傳媒中心。

